Class DataSegmentsWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.eutro.jwasm.BaseVisitor<DataSegmentsVisitor>
      • io.github.eutro.jwasm.DataSegmentsVisitor
        • io.github.eutro.jwasm.DataSegmentsWriter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ByteArrayConvertible, VectorWriter

    public class DataSegmentsWriter
extends DataSegmentsVisitor
implements VectorWriter
    A DataSegmentsVisitor that generates the corresponding WebAssembly bytecode as it is visited. This can be retrieved using VectorWriter.toByteArray() after visitEnd().
